query:
UPDATE cards
            SET
                card_type = COALESCE($2, card_type),
                expire_date = COALESCE($3, expire_date),
                cvv = COALESCE($4, cvv),
                card_provider = COALESCE($5, card_provider),
                updated_at = NOW()
            WHERE
                card_id = $1
                AND deleted_at IS NULL
            RETURNING 
                card_id,
                user_id,
                card_number,
                card_type,
                expire_date,
                cvv,
                card_provider,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                deleted_at
